{"type": "article", "id": 37164, "title": "Kate Spade要卖，以及，这款机械键盘很时尚 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-24T03:05:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1046, "name": "键盘"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 3154, "name": "Levi’s"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 20300, "name": "Asics Tiger"}, {"id": 37054, "name": "Côte&Ciel"}, {"id": 37057, "name": "Charles & Keith"}, {"id": 37058, "name": "BCBG"}, {"id": 3264, "name": "山本耀司"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 196, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170124094356OJzdeoaLqUSpu62k.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/markets/charles-keith-exits-japan-10763037/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>新加坡鞋包品牌 Charles &amp; Keith 关闭了它在日本的所有门店</b></a> | 在关店之前， Charles &amp; Keith 在日本的东京、大阪、名古屋等城市共有 13 家门店。从去年年底开始，它逐步退出了日本市场。宣称要集中精力发展电商网络以及其它国家市场。值得一说的是，这家公司在亚洲的其它市场发展地都很不错，有着“成为下一个 ZARA 或 H&amp;M”的野心。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/bcbg-to-shut-down-stores-and-focus-on-e-commerce/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国时装集团 BCBG 大规模关店，说要专注于电商</b></a> | 美国时装集团 BCBG Max Azria Group 由法国设计师  Max Azria 于 1989 年创办，它以出售小礼服、手提包和其他配饰为主。目前，BCBG 在全球有 570 家门店，美国有 175 家。据称，BCBG 现在的财务状况非常紧张，因而它计划关闭部分门店，对公司业务进行重组。它的发言人 Seth Lubove 表示，公司计划减少对实体店的投入，将发展重心转向授权经营、电商和批发销售渠道。</p><p class=\"\"><b>传：<a href=\"https://www.thestreet.com/story/13961980/1/coach-michael-kors-reportedly-interested-in-kate-spade.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach、MK 都有兴趣接手 Kate Spade，后者股价随之上涨</a></b> | 去年年底，Kate Spade 曾传出过因业绩不佳有意寻求买主的消息。上周五晚，彭博社消息称 Coach 和 Michael Kors 都有兴趣接受 Kate Spade。随后，Kate Spade 在这周周一的股价就上涨了 3.89%，至 18.45 每股。不过，这三方都对该消息不予置评。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">喜欢机械键盘又觉得它们长的不够时尚的话，这个叫 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/01/23/lofree-keyboard-typewriter/#slide-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lofree</a> 的机械键盘或许还不错。Lofree 可以把你的 Mac 或者 Windows 电脑变成一个有着圆形按钮的打字机。另外，它可以兼容 Windows、Mac、iOS 和 Android，最多可以对接三个设备，有三种不同的背光设置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101514dUzlm89So1YgnDPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101507oYmeUuEQDh5nlvkK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101507Qu3Anaxik4zg7Uq6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/adidas-y-3-2017-fall-winter-collection-paris\" rel=\"nofollow\">山本耀司发布全新 2017 秋冬系列 Y-3</a>，再一次将时装与运动风格充分融合，以黑色和绿色为主调，搭配更具前卫感的剪裁和镂空、拉链、飘带、满版印花等细节，整个系列极富层次感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542EbHXm8LjnPFfVBWY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542uQrI7iDO8oRe6jgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701241015428zpNLtGKf3CVTPWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542Fh9E5cwnmuydS2Pe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542784hXS9O0lM6WtEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701241015427OWsSVyGFER4UALk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542YCFtRhx8pjHTmZG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101542uLZ1XyFsCEVSKQ9T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101543pRLfSzrhIFxseNGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101543a9gAujL0qSXRJUMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701241015432znUNLQ9CIXqm1MY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101543wnYuv8PkiqcERtCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101601KWQ89svfLuwZDAbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101601GfArHdXyS2e4C5Bm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101601Am9Hc1gwxpML53Nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101601tGNHV1WU6bl5OvzT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101601WPw2TiNdUpzIo0bF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/asics-gel-sight-taupe-carbon-grey\" rel=\"nofollow\">ASICS Tiger 为经典的 GEL-Sight 推出以灰色为主打色调的新设计</a>，鞋身主体以灰调呈现，加上蓝色和粉色做点缀，并不会觉得沉闷无聊。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101334DHFKc7eEBoGjyxgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101334FnYxa5y1VAXQPN3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/levis-cny-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Levi’s 发布鸡年主题服饰</a>。该系列包括洗水牛仔裤、牛仔外套和 T-shirt，以及一款色彩丰富的双面纪念夹克。其中，</font>公鸡的图案作为点缀，以卡通方法呈现在绣章及印花上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101613VrN6TX5CwxscJuLK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101620FtfvM65J7a3cCUrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101621Fayp2EClJ578udon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101621EfiUGXdq0lFsckMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101625kMzKJU9YCSRnjsi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">法国箱包品牌 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.coteetciel.com/en-HK/shop/bags\" rel=\"nofollow\">Côte&amp;Ciel</a> 推出了全新的背包 TIGRIS。TIGRIS 以十九世纪阿尔卑斯山上搬运工人的掀盖包袋为原型，在简约的长型掀盖袋款于掀盖中加入收纳袋，还附有卷轴式的可收纳防水帽。这次推出的 TIGRIS 共有三款不同的布料可选，包括环保尼龙，复古味十足的上蜡帆布，以及全牛皮素材。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701241016365xA9s3LY0RoeatlO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101636POjFR8Wy7kBzCiYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170124101636Su3OIdsbvCNjM9Qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/01/23/lofree-keyboard-typewriter/#slide-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">hisnobiety</a></p>"}